name: Door to Heaven
description: Millions of light years away from the Earth, Astronaut on a vast planet, made of forests with only grass and Cherry Blossom trees, covered with mist all over the planet. The wanderer discovers a door that is directly connected to the Heaven with pinkish clouds coming to the swamp planet. Here, the astronaut is playing the role of the naive people of the Earth who want to discover a way to heaven without thinking about the limitations of the nature. To satisfy their needs they will break the limitations of the nature and harm the whole mankind for their greed.
